channel.title: Need Help someone with VPS Exp
channel.description:
Ok I was coding today and then out of no where my vps freezes turns blank it closes then I try to connect to it again (through RDP) and it says
This Computer cannot connect to the remote computer
Try again or contact owner of the computer
I have a Windows 64 bit vps and it just got setup today but my server is still running but I cant code lol.

item.title: Need Help someone with VPS Exp
item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

Sounds like multiple connections to a VPS that’s only meant to handle one connection caused your VPS to time out. It should be back to normal in a few hrs. Don’t try to connect via RDC for awhile though. Let it drop old connections.

Orrr, it could have just crashed. >.>
